WARNING on Automatic screen activation hacks
********************************************

   WARNING:  You should not use illegal hacks of the "Automatically
activate any screen that is ever in front" variety.  This is simply
improper and just won't do.  Hacks like this will not crash Chaos but
they will cause it to behave in an annoying manner since hacks of this
nature will constantly activate the WRONG screen.  Do not use
"AutoActivate FrontMost Screen" hacks.

   Failure to heed the above warning may cause the screen scrolling to
stop working.  This will prevent you from reading certain lengthy spell
descriptions.

   MCP has such a hack.  It should be turned off when playing Chaos.


