     if something is a Meditation. If its a Meditation and its empty
     then anyone can enter it, even if the meditation is a creature
     that belongs to someone else. Ok I just added in the line of code
     to prevent human wizards from mounting enemy meditation creatures.
     But now I am thinking I should have just left it the way it was.
     It sounds pretty cool that you can mount an enemy magic carpet in
     an emergency. You should eventually get a bonus spell out of it.
